---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Radar Digital" description="Seu radar de tendências em marketing digital, inteligência artificial e monetização — análises, estratégias e ferramentas para crescer no digital.">
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center pt-20 overflow-hidden bg-surface transition-colors duration-300">
    <!-- Background glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full opacity-15 blur-3xl pointer-events-none" 
         style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.3) 0%, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1) 40%, transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full opacity-10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
         style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2) 0%, transparent 60%);"></div>

    <!-- Radar animation SVG -->
    <div class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04] dark:opacity-[0.04] opacity-[0.07]">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 500 500" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="240" stroke="#00e5ff" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 8"/>
        <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="180" stroke="#00e5ff" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 8"/>
        <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="120" stroke="#00e5ff" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 8"/>
        <circle cx="250" cy="250" r="60" stroke="#00e5ff" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="4 8"/>
        <line x1="250" y1="250" x2="250" y2="10" stroke="#00e5ff" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3">
          <animateTransform attributeName="transform" type="rotate" from="0 250 250" to="360 250 250" dur="8s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
        </line>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 w-full relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <!-- Tag -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 animate-pulse-cyan"></span>
          <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-500/80 font-medium">Seu Radar de Tendências</span>
        </div>

        <!-- Main title -->
        <h1 class="text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[1.05] tracking-tight">
          <span class="text-text-primary transition-colors">Radar</span>
          <br />
          <span class="gradient-text">Digital</span>
        </h1>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-text-secondary mt-6 max-w-xl leading-relaxed transition-colors">
          Marketing digital, inteligência artificial e monetização — 
          <span class="text-text-primary">o que realmente funciona, explicado sem enrolação.</span>
        </p>

        <!-- CTAs -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-10">
          <a href="#categorias" 
             class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm 
                    bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-500 border border-cyan-500/30 
                    hover:bg-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
            Explorar Categorias
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#artigos" 
             class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm 
                    text-text-secondary border border-surface hover:border-cyan-500/30 hover:text-cyan-500
                    transition-all duration-300">
            Últimos Artigos
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats row -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 md:gap-12 mt-16 pt-10 border-t transition-colors duration-300" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary transition-colors">3</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-0.5 transition-colors">Categorias</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary transition-colors">0</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-0.5 transition-colors">Artigos</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary transition-colors">
            <div>100%</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-0.5 font-normal transition-colors">Sem enrolação</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- CATEGORIAS -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="categorias" class="py-24 relative bg-surface transition-colors duration-300">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="tag-pill">Navegue por tema</span>
        <h2 class="section-title mt-4 text-text-primary transition-colors">Três pilares, um <span class="text-cyan-500">radar</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto">
          Tudo que você precisa para dominar o marketing digital, entender IA e construir fontes de renda reais.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1: Marketing Digital -->
        <a href="/marketing-digital" class="glass-card p-8 group glow-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-cyan-500/20 transition-all">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 3v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 16.5h2.25M3.75 3h-1.5m1.5 0h16.5m0 0h1.5m-1.5 0v11.25A2.25 2.25 0 0118 16.5h-2.25m-7.5 0h7.5m-7.5 0l-1 3m8.5-3l1 3m0 0l.5 1.5m-.5-1.5h-9.5m0 0l-.5 1.5m.75-9l3-3 2.148 2.148A12.061 12.061 0 0116.5 7.605" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary transition-colors mb-2">Marketing Digital</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary transition-colors leading-relaxed mb-5">SEO, tráfego pago, redes sociais, email marketing, funis de venda e estratégias que geram resultados mensuráveis.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-cyan-500 text-sm font-medium">
            Explorar
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 2: Inteligência Artificial -->
        <a href="/inteligencia-artificial" class="glass-card p-8 group glow-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-purple-500/20 transition-all">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.455 2.456L21.75 6l-1.036.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455 2.456zM16.894 20.567L16.5 21.75l-.394-1.183a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423-1.423L13.5 18.75l1.183-.394a2.25 2.25 0 001.423-1.423l.394-1.183.394 1.183a2.25 2.25 0 001.423 1.423l1.183.394-1.183.394a2.25 2.25 0 00-1.423 1.423z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary transition-colors mb-2">Inteligência Artificial</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary transition-colors leading-relaxed mb-5">Ferramentas de IA, automação, chatbots, geração de conteúdo e como aplicar machine learning no seu negócio.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-purple-500 text-sm font-medium">
            Explorar
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 3: Monetização -->
        <a href="/monetizacao" class="glass-card p-8 group glow-border">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-amber-500/20 transition-all">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-text-primary transition-colors mb-2">Monetização</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary transition-colors leading-relaxed mb-5">Infoprodutos, afiliados, assinaturas, dropshipping, publicidade digital e modelos de negócio escaláveis.</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-amber-500 text-sm font-medium">
            Explorar
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- ÚLTIMOS ARTIGOS -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="artigos" class="py-24 relative bg-surface transition-colors duration-300">
    <!-- Background subtle divider -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-cyan-500/[0.02] to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-14">
        <div>
          <span class="tag-pill">Conteúdo recente</span>
          <h2 class="section-title mt-4 text-text-primary transition-colors">Últimos do <span class="text-cyan-500">Radar</span></h2>
        </div>
        <a href="/artigos" class="hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-secondary hover:text-cyan-500 transition-colors">
          Ver todos
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Placeholder articles grid -->
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Article card placeholder 1 -->
        <article class="glass-card overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 via-blue-600/5 to-surface-elevated flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-text-muted transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 7.5h1.5m-1.5 3h1.5m-7.5 3h7.5m-7.5 3h7.5m3-9h3.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V18a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25M16.5 7.5V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25M16.5 7.5V4.875c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H4.125C3.504 3.75 3 4.254 3 4.875V18a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h13.5M6 7.5h3v3H6v-3z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-md text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider bg-surface-elevated text-text-muted transition-colors mb-3">Em breve</span>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary group-hover:text-cyan-500 transition-colors">Primeiro artigo sendo escrito</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2 leading-relaxed transition-colors">O Radar Digital está captando sinais. Em breve, conteúdo fresco sobre marketing, IA e monetização.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article card placeholder 2 -->
        <article class="glass-card overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 via-pink-600/5 to-surface-elevated flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-text-muted transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-md text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider bg-surface-elevated text-text-muted transition-colors mb-3">Em breve</span>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary group-hover:text-purple-500 transition-colors">Ferramentas de IA explicadas</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2 leading-relaxed transition-colors">Análises práticas de ferramentas de IA — o que realmente entrega valor vs. hype.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Article card placeholder 3 -->
        <article class="glass-card overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="h-44 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500/10 via-orange-600/5 to-surface-elevated flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-text-muted transition-colors" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m0 0v9m0-9h-1.5m0 0h-1.5m6 0h-1.5m0 0h-1.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5">
            <span class="inline-block px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-md text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider bg-surface-elevated text-text-muted transition-colors mb-3">Em breve</span>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary group-hover:text-amber-500 transition-colors">Estratégias de monetização</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-2 leading-relaxed transition-colors">Modelos de negócio digital que geram receita — de afiliados a infoprodutos.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <!-- Mobile "ver todos" -->
      <div class="mt-8 text-center sm:hidden">
        <a href="/artigos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-cyan-500 hover:text-cyan-400 transition-colors">
          Ver todos os artigos
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- NEWSLETTER -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="py-24 relative bg-surface transition-colors duration-300">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="glass-card p-10 md:p-16 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto glow-border relative overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Decorative dots -->
        <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-40 h-40 opacity-[0.04] dark:opacity-[0.04] opacity-[0.08]">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/><circle cx="30" cy="10" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/>
            <circle cx="50" cy="10" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/><circle cx="70" cy="10" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/>
            <circle cx="90" cy="10" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/><circle cx="10" cy="30" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/>
            <circle cx="30" cy="30" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/><circle cx="50" cy="30" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/>
            <circle cx="70" cy="30" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/><circle cx="90" cy="30" r="2" fill="#00e5ff"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <span class="tag-pill">Fique ligado</span>
          <h2 class="section-title mt-4 text-text-primary transition-colors">Receba o <span class="text-cyan-500">sinal</span></h2>
          <p class="text-text-secondary mt-3 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm leading-relaxed transition-colors">
            Assine e seja o primeiro a saber quando novos artigos chegarem no Radar Digital. Sem spam, só conteúdo de verdade.
          </p>

          <form class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 max-w-md mx-auto" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Newsletter em breve! 🚀')">
            <input 
              type="email" 
              placeholder="seu@email.com" 
              class="flex-1 px-5 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm transition-all duration-300"
              style="background: var(--color-surface-elevated); color: var(--color-text-primary); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"
              required
            />
            <button 
              type="submit" 
              class="px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500/20 to-cyan-600/20 
                     border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-500 text-sm font-semibold
                     hover:from-cyan-500/30 hover:to-cyan-600/30 hover:border-cyan-500/50
                     transition-all duration-300">
              Assinar
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- CTA FINAL -->
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pb-24 bg-surface transition-colors duration-300">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-3 transition-colors">Radar Digital © 2026</p>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm max-w-md mx-auto transition-colors">
        Feito por <span class="text-text-primary">Francisco Silva</span> — captando sinais, entregando valor.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
